data.description: End Unit with Maxxed out Upgrades! 6 year new townhouse boasts all of the bells and whistles this Ryan Homes Townhouse could offer! Set deep into the community for privacy and close to the end of the street for ample guest parking, this oasis backs to the woods and is perfect for a family or professionals. Enter thru the lower level into the spacious foyer. The garage to the left can be used for parking or storage with built in shelving. A half bath and wet bar with granite counter tops are convenient additions to this room that could be used as a bedroom/in law suite or family room and has sliders for outdoor access with wooded views. The main level kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops that match those of the wet bar on the first floor, ample storage, extended 8 ft island, space for eat in kitchen table and additional square footage where the breakfast nook/coffee bar bumps out in front of the deck. This unit features a larger deck with ample space for grilling/entertaining. Off the kitchen the open concept floor plan features a family room with fireplace and high ceilings. Find all three bedrooms on the Upper level. The primary bedroom has large walk in closet and ensuite bathroom featuring soaking tub, double sink vanity and updated tile. Another great upgrade is the upper level laundry room, compete with utility tub and storage. Find two additional spacious bedrooms to complete the third floor! Hardwood flooring, central vacuum system, and 5.1 built in surround are additional amenities. Easy access to highways AC expressway/route 42. Walking path to local stores/The Shoppes at Crosskeys. Meticulously maintained community w/Large grass common area/field. Make your appointment today this one will not last!
